	"FriendlyName": "EOS System",
	"Description": "Standalone EOS (Epic Online Services) system for Satisfactory dedicated servers. Implements all EOS interfaces from scratch using only the raw EOS C SDK DLL — no dependency on the engine EOSSDK/EOSShared modules. Provides: Platform init, Connect/PUID lookup, Sessions, AntiCheat, Sanctions, Stats, Achievements, Leaderboards, Player Data Storage, Title Storage, Metrics, Reports, Ecom, Friends, Presence, and UserInfo.",
